text: Akhunovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Mechetlinsky Selsoviet, Salavatsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 673 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 18 km from Maloyaz, 6 km from Mechetlino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Salavatsky District
title: Akhunovo, Salavatsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
